Source:
  Title: A Year with Rumi
  Translator: Coleman Barks
  Author: Rumi
  ISBN: 978-0060845971
  Publisher: HarperOne
Format: Verse
By: Rumi
Title: Don't Let Your Throat Tighten
Description: January 7
---
Don't let your throat tighten
with fear. Take sips of breath
all day and night, before death
closes your mouth.
